26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a9442f30\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.fifa.com/fifa-world-ranking/ranking-table/men/index.html</a></blockquote><br />\n好波</blockquote><br />\n但其實又點肯定正選個啲係精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：純討論 無惡意</blockquote><br />\n好簡單，洋大哥當年係申花重點陪訓嘅球員，結果因為冇錢疏通而冇得踢，咁你話宜家中國國家隊入面有幾多真係精英？"},{"pid":"7cf4f82f8d7f671139e5b0625db453f46165ce75","tid":149450,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"人多冇用<br />\n<br />\n美國1個Steve Jobs, 好過你中國1000個馬雲"},{"pid":"faae13f2c9071f5acdf301feab95fca0e62b6379","tid":149450,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"事實勝於雄辯<br />\n支那有冇1%精英，睇得出<br />\n美國都冇1%精英啦，知唔知一百份一係幾多？<br />\n小學生未教小數點？"},{"pid":"3500527d0430e74d8e2db8ac73e8bb7531945001","tid":149450,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人多冇用<br />\n<br />\n美國1個Steve Jobs, 好過你中國1000個馬雲</blockquote><br />\n支那嗰1000個馬雲係抄同一個個馬雲<br />\n之後互搶生意"},{"pid":"d5d7f8a6fd01e3174f2b423efb17288942b7520c","tid":149450,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5313048e401f792ebb8dcbc08f435e00a7b555c","tid":149450,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"廢青吹水post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4436e55e441c1a34990396a5280a4cf24b0f755","tid":149450,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"14億可能真係有好多精英, 卻無乜邊個可以靠關係上位呢"},{"pid":"a114327f9fe4971f7c2523416d0bae66b8bc2374","tid":149450,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"因為中國個99%會諗辦法做低個1%"},{"pid":"5881b0dd7f433bef0c3ca86e506b82bb23b6b280","tid":149450,"uid":1841