%2Fm.fifa.com%2Ffifa-world-ranking%2Franking-table%2Fmen%2Findex.html&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn026kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a9442f30\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.fifa.com/fifa-world-ranking/ranking-table/men/index.html</a></blockquote><br />\n好波</blockquote><br />\n其實為什麼中國的國企開放改革時不肯面對全世界嘅競爭?<br />\n<br />\n咁為什麼香港人未準備好，以及政策未有保護香港人之下，<br />\n<br />\n就要面對全中國14億人嘅競爭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f27514835a0c04690def8a41041fc7e1b7c7d5","tid":149450,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}